ZH: 我们可以步行去公园。
EN: We can walk to the park.

ZH: 爸爸每天早上步行去上班。
EN: My dad walks to work every morning.

ZH: 他喜欢步行，因为可以欣赏风景。
EN: He enjoys walking because he can enjoy the scenery.

ZH: 好多人选择步行上班，因为比较健康。
EN: Many people choose to walk to work because it's healthier.

ZH: 我步行走了半个小时才到学校。
EN: It took me half an hour to walk to school.

ZH: 大家都鼓励多多步行，保持身体健康。
EN: Everyone encourages walking more to stay healthy.

ZH: 她步行去超市买东西。
EN: She walks to the supermarket to buy groceries.

ZH: 据说步行对心脏很好。
EN: Walking is said to be good for the heart.

ZH: 这里附近有很多步行道。
EN: There are many walking trails nearby.

ZH: 我喜欢步行，因为可以放松。
EN: I like walking because it helps me relax.

ZH: 他计划步行穿越整个乡村。
EN: He plans to walk through the entire countryside.

ZH: 我们步行去看电影吧。
EN: Let's walk to the movies.

ZH: 走路可以锻炼腿部肌肉。
EN: Walking can exercise leg muscles.

ZH: 我妈妈每天步行散步。
EN: My mom takes a walk every day.

ZH: 步行是一种环保的出行方式。
EN: Walking is an eco-friendly mode of transportation.

ZH: 爷爷喜欢早上步行锻炼。
EN: Grandpa enjoys exercising by walking in the morning.

ZH: 他步行去图书馆借书。
EN: He walks to the library to borrow books.

ZH: 这个城市有很多步行街。
EN: This city has many pedestrian streets.

ZH: 我喜欢步行，因为可以呼吸新鲜空气。
EN: I like walking because I can breathe fresh air.

ZH: 他步行爬上了山顶。
EN: He walked up to the top of the hill.
